    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "周廣順三年春，樞密使王峻遙鎮青州，有司制旄節以備迎授。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "前夕，其節有聲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "主者曰：「昔後唐長興中，安重誨授河中，其節亦有聲，斯亦木之妖也。」",
          "translations": [
